{"tid":897184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"作家馬建抵港：大館後面可能有更大黑手","createTime":"2018-11-10T16:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T16:52:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"177196c1ebfe47058f3c39b770422ae7c1465961","tid":897184,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"作家馬建抵港：大館後面可能有更大黑手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lq0c6lkK8wA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLq0c6lkK8wA&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6a1cb14b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lq0c6lkK8wA</a><br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\nPublished on Nov 9, 2018<br />\n<br />\n作家馬建抵港：大館後面可能有更大黑手<br />\n<br />\n居於英國的中國作家馬建，周五傍晚從倫敦飛抵香港，成功入境準備出席周六舉行的香港國際文學節講座。馬建步出機場禁區接受傳媒訪問時，大館仍未宣布讓馬建的講座如期舉行，第二個場地中環The Annex所屬的南豐集團稱「不會是相關活動的舉辦場地，與活動或作者並無關係」。<br />\n<br />\n馬建向記者質疑：「第二個地點也被取消，看來問題不是大館負責人一個人的問題，可能大館後面有一個更大的黑手，是他在控制這個講座，認為講座不應該發出聲音來，讓我非常生氣。」、「可能不是他（大館），他只是一個傀儡，他只是一個傳話筒，背後可能有更大的東西通知它。」<br />\n<br />\n全文閱讀：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QtLAXW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QtLAXW&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c789109d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QtLAXW</a><br />\n<br />\n眾新聞網站：<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com&d=INALvyyzIH9cpXQf1t%2F%2BEghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bc3df075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com</a>"},{"pid":"a1b4d849b4c1e180bfb3e26a5c82b9ad8d344eb4","tid":897184,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"講埋西環都無死錯人喇<br />\n<br />\n香港好快連公開閙共產黨都要拉架喇"}]}